text: Novoalexeyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakibashevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Kirgiz- Miyaki, 8 km from Anyasevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Novoalexeyevka, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
